115
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,880
He's going to host the exhibition.

116
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,400
When will he be back?

117
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,480
He told me

118
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,520
