Maybe even half a year.

122
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,440
I'm not sure.

123
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,080
It's okay.

124
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,000
He'll be back eventually.

125
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,600
Or, do you not want to be

126
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,560
