127
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,320
No, it's all work.

128
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,720
It's the same for me.

129
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,600
Have you had breakfast?

130
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,600
Gu Chuan left me some breakfast

131
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,400
