(Why leave without saying goodbye?)

142
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,840
(Is he trying to avoid me on purpose?)

143
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,640
(Does he)

144
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,200
(hate seeing me)

145
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,320
(that much?)

