219
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:34,760
Xu Cheng Ran.

220
00:11:34,920 --> 00:11:36,400
What did you promise me before?

221
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:37,000
Didn't you say

222
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,600
